{"tid":1869274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"在武漢的美國公民感染新型肺炎死亡","createTime":"2020-02-08T05:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T05:58:11.000Z","uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"23d9fd93073d3b0a15203720008e7fcab81e8076","tid":1869274,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:46:46.000Z","msg":"美國駐華大使館證實，一名在武漢的美國公民，因為新型冠狀病毒死亡。<br />\n<br />\n使館人員說，死者60歲，前日在醫院不治，對家屬致以深切哀悼，但拒絕透露死者性別等詳情。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部昨日表示，19名外國人在中國感染新型肺炎，但未有交代患者的國籍。<br />\n<br />\n內地至今有超過34000宗確診病例，722人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507411-20200208.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507411-20200208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOmipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=9f16ade7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507411-20200208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4dc8bdfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507411-20200208.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7c19f647804ea942cbedf6eb82b02bc7aa2b34c4","tid":1869274,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"6ca1b617bc08c9b4d19c84b3aad8de56d3514a68","tid":1869274,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"九成係中国移民"},{"pid":"4a6c7c6c68dc67785d68fa28a58c877149d1154f","tid":1869274,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23d9fd93073d3b0a15203720008e7fcab81e8076","tid":1869274,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T05:46:46.000Z","msg":"美國駐華大使館證實，一名在武漢的美國公民，因為新型冠狀病毒死亡。<br />\n<br />\n使館人員說，死者60歲，前日在醫院不治，對家屬致以深切哀悼，但拒絕透露死者性別等詳情。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部昨日表示，19名外國人在中國感染新型肺炎，但未有交代患者的國籍。<br />\n<br />\n內地至今有超過34000宗確診病例，722人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://